title: Macadamia nut banana bread
ingredients: ['100g butter, at room temperature', '100g caster sugar', '2 eggs, at room temperature', '550g pureed ripe bananas', '1 1/4 teaspoons bicarbonate of soda', '1/2 teaspoon baking powder', '1/4 teaspoon coarse sea salt', '1/2 teaspoon vanilla extract', '250g plain flour', '60g coarsely chopped macadamia nuts']
